```plantuml
@startuml Elkinmt19_feature-hero-ml

actor User
participant "Data Pipeline" as DataPipeline
participant "Feature Store (Feast)" as Feast
participant "Online Store (Redis)" as Redis
participant "Offline Store (Parquet)" as Parquet
participant "ML Model" as MLModel

User -> DataPipeline: Triggers data ingestion
DataPipeline -> Feast: Registers feature definitions
Feast -> DataPipeline: Acknowledges registration

DataPipeline -> DataPipeline: Fetches raw data
DataPipeline -> DataPipeline: Transforms data
DataPipeline -> Feast: Ingests features
Feast -> Redis: Stores features (online)
Feast -> Parquet: Stores features (offline)

User -> MLModel: Requests prediction
MLModel -> Feast: Requests features (online)
Feast -> Redis: Retrieves features
Redis -> Feast: Returns features
Feast -> MLModel: Returns features
MLModel -> User: Returns prediction

User -> MLModel: Requests batch prediction
MLModel -> Feast: Requests features (offline)
Feast -> Parquet: Retrieves features
Parquet -> Feast: Returns features
Feast -> MLModel: Returns features
MLModel -> User: Returns predictions

@enduml
```